  <li>Be prepared for your check-in - tag your instructor in a PR using <a href="https://gist.github.com/ameseee/bcad94e879ff60e8649820c8e321d58a">this template</a> by 8am on Thursday, October 4.</li>
  <li>To submit, tag your instructor in a PR using <a href="https://gist.github.com/ameseee/c4f0b2e1bb3f41661a7de8574ba3992c">this template</a>.</li>
</ul>

